# Cloudflare Pages routing for wearthemood.com
#
# On the DigitalOcean droplet, Caddy reverse-proxies /r/* to the API container
# (deploy/Caddyfile: `handle /r/* { reverse_proxy api:8000 }`). Cloudflare Pages
# serves static assets only, so without this rule every referral link would 404
# the moment the apex is pointed at Pages — silently breaking install attribution
# (§24) for every share already in the wild.
#
# Pages `_redirects` cannot transparently proxy to another origin, so this is a
# 302 to the API, which records the attribution and then issues its own redirect.
# One extra hop versus Caddy's reverse-proxy; the referral code is preserved.
/r/*    https://api.wearthemood.com/r/:splat    302

